English:  Death act of Princess Joséphine of Belgium (born 18th january 1871) laid under the authority of Burgomaster Jules Anspach, Civil Record Officer of Brussels

18 January 1871


Source

État civil de la Ville de Bruxelles, actes de décès de 1871, 19 janvier 1871 (open a "familysearch.org" account to read the link).


Author

Jules Anspach, Bourgmestre de Bruxelles de 1863 à 1879, Officier d'État Civil de Bruxelles
